column1: #Text=Let none stand amazed at the pageantry of false Churches,
#Text=nor value the Whore of Rome because of her bravery.
#Text=Pearles and precious stones, but smells strong of Aegypt.
#Text=the Persumes of Arabia can ' t hide or choak her stink
#Text=Lateran Musick will consecrate her Masses into audience, nor her
#Text=incense procure access to the Throne of Grace,
#Text=I will not smell says the Lord in your Solemn Assemblies.
#Text=your Songs, the melody of your Viols, let judgment run
#Text=down as waters and righteousness like a mighty stream.
